    "Data augmentation, regularization (dropout, weight decay), and advanced optimization algorithms (Adam, RMSprop) are examples.",
    "Pretraining on ImageNet and transfer learning 43, 44 have also been used to initialize ViT models.",
    "Hybrid models.",
    "Hybrid designs integrate Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Vision Transformers (ViTs) for tasks such as pneumonia detection in chest X-ray images, we first use a CNN as the feature extractor, removing its fully connected layers while retaining its convolutional and pooling layers.",
    "The CNN-generated feature maps are then separated into non-overlapping patches, and each patch is converted into a high-dimensional embedding vector."
